| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5800 — Mass File Rename (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3a98e93e-0de1-5bbe-8f39-2dde3dacfdc9"
